               <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">This section is applicable if A12_FloorSlabArea  GT 0 And  If A13_ProjectScopeAddition includes at least one of the following: AdditionLTE300, AdditionGT300LTE400, AdditionGT400LTE700, AdditionGT700LTE1000,  AdditionLTE300ADU, AdditionGT300LTE400ADU, AdditionGT400LTE700ADU, Or AdditionGT700LTE1000ADU.  If A13_ProjectScopeAddition == AdditionGT700LTE1000ADU, display section but  entry is optional.   If insulation is required because of slab type and project climate zone, then user is required to enter either all R-values or all U-factors in the appropriate fields</xs:documentation>
               
               
               <xs:documentation source="MinOccurs">If this section doesn't apply, display only the section FieldText and the statement 'This section does not apply to this project.'</xs:documentation>
               
            
