                                          <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">User selects from list: NFRCRated, display text: NFRC;  CECDefaultPerformance, display term Tables 110.6A and 110.6B;  NA6Equations, display term Equations NA6-1 and NA6-2; and CF1R_ENV_02 display term Area-weighted Average Worksheet (CF1R-ENV-02)</xs:documentation>
                                          
                                       
                                       </xs:annotation>
                                       
                                    
